textAnnotations.description:
CONTRAINDICATION
This product may cause an increase in your normal bowel
movements, reduce the dosage if this happens.
COMPOSITION
Stinging nettle, Pygeum, Saw palmetto, Viscum album
CAUTION
Do not use if seal is broken
Discontinue use if you experience any adverse effect
